Net/FreeDB version 0.08
=======================

Net::FreeDB is an oo-based module to interface
with FreeDB servers.  It also includes some basic
cdrom methods to generate a cddbid and get the
required disc information required for a FreeDB
query call.  These cdrom-based methods are provided
as both static and method calls.  Currently this
functionality only works on Linux and Windows.  If
you have an OS you'd like to add, please let me know.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

	Net::Cmd:   2.12 or higher
	CDDB::File: 1.01 or higher
	File::Temp: 0.05 or higher

